	<message label="101" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Eh" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡Holi, <20_2 arg="8" /><tag a="110" b="3" />! <anim id="Greeting" target="subNpc" targetSpec="" />Le estaba preguntando a <tag a="110" b="31" arg="0xcd01" /> qué deporte le gusta practicar.<anim id="Nodding" target="player" targetSpec="" /></message>
	<message label="102" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Como <tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x5 0xcd00 0x8 0x62 0x75 0x65 0x6e 0xa 0x62 0x75 0x65 0x6e 0x61 0x0" /> <tag a="110" b="15" /> tonificad<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x5 0xcd00 0x2 0x6f 0x2 0x61 0x0" /> que soy,<delay8 /> yo practico de todo.<pageBreak /><20_2 arg="4" />Pero ahora estoy superenganchad<tag a="50" b="17" arg="0x5 0xcd00 0x2 0x6f 0x2 0x61 0x0" />
en practicar<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay8 /> <anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />!</message>
	<message label="103" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />¡Fenomenal!<delay20 /><20_2 arg="3" /> <anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />Pues la próxima
